WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:02.665
Every year around the same period,...

00:03.100 --> 00:04.575
...December through March,...

00:05.055 --> 00:11.070
...they install a huge ice rink in front of the Hotel de Ville, town hall,...

00:11.700 --> 00:15.980
...where Parisians can skate for free until midnight.

00:17.220 --> 00:20.660
That is, providing you have your own blades, of course.

00:20.950 --> 00:23.455
Otherwise, you have to rent some.

00:24.120 --> 00:25.495
I love the idea...

00:25.825 --> 00:27.925
...even if I only tried it once!

